@ericzolf I found the problem.

The `tuning` plugin is missing in the config file. You should be able to add `{
         "type": "tuning"
      },` under the plugins section in `/etc/cni/net.d/<netname>.conflist`. After that you should be able to set a static mac with this network.

I opened #8467 to include this by default in the future.
